#
# The columns are aligned but the reading routines allow for some flexibility - it is sufficient to use blanks to separate horizontal entries
# The '#' sign indicates a comment and is ignored
#
#  Ref.  experiment    units              value        Energy        value         error                  Z.A sec   |     Z.A pri    [comments]
#                    X      Y              name   <E>   low    high    number    -        +
